            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-nav__box">
          <a href="" class="hover:600 label-m footer-nav__link">Кейсы</a>
          <div class="c-grey-6 footer-nav__list">
            <a href="" class="hover:600 label-m footer-nav__link">
              Веб скрапинг
            </a>
            <a href="" class="hover:600 label-m footer-nav__link">E-commerce</a>
            <a href="" class="hover:600 label-m footer-nav__link">SEO & SERP</a>
            <a href="" class="hover:600 label-m footer-nav__link">
